WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script3 — Hmoob

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Nyob zoo!

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:05.900
Tawv nqaij uas kov koj lub cuab hloov los yog cuab yeej xav tau kev saib xyuas tshwj xeeb.

3
00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:09.227
Kev ntxuav tawv nqaij zoo tiv thaiv feem ntau cov teeb meem.

4
00:00:09.227 --> 00:00:11.483
Nov yog cov yam uas zoo uas yuav tsum ua.

5
00:00:12.883 --> 00:00:14.634
Kev ntxuav txhua hnub.

6
00:00:14.584 --> 00:00:19.838
Txhua hmo, ntxuav tawv nqaij uas kov koj lub cuab yeej nrog dej sov thiab xab npum maj mam pH neutral.

7
00:00:19.838 --> 00:00:23.885
Ntxuav kom huv si thiab so qhuav maj mam nrog kev npog, tsis txhob txhuam.

8
00:00:23.885 --> 00:00:25.802
Kauj ruam no yog tseem ceeb heev.

9
00:00:27.202 --> 00:00:28.720
Kev tiv thaiv.

10
00:00:28.670 --> 00:00:33.066
Ua tawv nqaij muag tom qab ntxuav, tab sis tsis txhob ntxuav ua ntej tso lub cuab yeej.

11
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:37.974
Tsis txhob cia tawv nqaij pliaj hauv lub cuab yeej, thiab hnav lub ris tsho hauv paus haum zoo tsis muaj kev xaws tuab.

12
00:00:39.374 --> 00:00:41.065
Cov tsos ceeb toom.

13
00:00:41.015 --> 00:00:49.179
Hu rau peb tam sim no yog koj pom liab ntau dua nees nkaum feeb, qhov raug, qhov mob ntswg, tsw txawv los yog nab puv tshaj qhov ib txwm muaj.

14
00:00:49.179 --> 00:00:51.191
Tsis txhob tsis quav ntsej cov tsos no.

15
00:00:52.591 --> 00:00:54.988
Koj txoj kev zoo yog peb qhov tseem ceeb.

16
00:00:54.938 --> 00:00:57.841
Peb pab neeg nyob ntawm no los nrog koj txhua kauj ruam.

17
00:00:57.841 --> 00:00:59.949
Tsis txhob hesitate hu rau peb.
